thread.title_full: Spa World Australia Pty Ltd reviewed by craig

author: craig
title: craig
text:
“I purchased a Vortex Aqualap Pro Plus swim spa recently from Elaine at Spa World. After speaking to Elaine in the showroom I decided to take the plunge and with no regrets. The delivery and locating the spa was easy and with our electrician's help we had the spa operational 3 days later. Nothing but pleasure since easy to maintain. Water chemicals are simple. Swimming against the swim jets takes a while to get used to.
What made all this easy and stress free? Elaine from Spa World Campbell Town, NSW”
